{"tid":28426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胚胎入稟告荷李活女星👶🏼","createTime":"2016-12-08T02:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T06:16:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a01a56e9463a557d1dfdb6c44c5a50c726f67ee4","tid":28426,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:38:43.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】荷李活女星蘇菲亞維格拉（Sofia Vergara，圖右）被前未婚夫以兩人的胚胎名義入稟控告，指控她企圖剝奪出生權利。如果獲受理，將創下未出生者成為原告的先例。 <br />\n<br />\n前男友爭擁有權掀官司<br />\n<br />\n44歲的《摩登家庭》哥倫比亞裔女星蘇菲亞維格拉以4300萬美元（約3.3億港元）收入，連續5年稱霸美國財經雜誌《福布斯》最賺錢電視女星排行榜。<br />\n<br />\n蘇菲亞與前未婚夫、41歲商人洛布（Nick Loeb，圖左）在2013年起擁有兩個冷凍胚胎至今，兩人2014年分手後，開始爭奪胚胎擁有權。<br />\n<br />\n去年結婚的蘇菲亞曾表示，希望孩子出生於一個有愛的關係中，因此希望這兩個胚胎無限期冷凍。<br />\n<br />\n洛布則要求兩個胚胎能夠由代母誕下，因此周二以兩個胚胎的名義，入稟向來支持生命權的路易斯安那州法院，質疑蘇菲亞不准他們出生，是剝奪他們的生存權和享用兩人當年成立基金的權利。<br />\n<br />\n（紐約郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161208/s00014/1481133256476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161208%2Fs00014%2F1481133256476&d=7zzUWbBCWXR1ISRxLjE2bAv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=52a1ea0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161208%2Fs00014%2F1481133256476&h=49c142fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161208/s00014/1481133256476</a>"},{"pid":"8c9de56d98c82951bd8bd6c7aa131bcab4f8fed0","tid":28426,"uid":32650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:14:29.000Z","msg":"佢好撚正"},{"pid":"6451bcd7308a2f4e8227acf29f42ea21b5dfbc6f","tid":28426,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:20:14.000Z","msg":"咁都有得告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55383b835d91a941fbaf9a00de985d012addf12","tid":28426,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.boomsbeat